    "basmil_image_richtext_aJUzbg": {
      "type": "basmil-image-richtext",
      "blocks": {
        "content_thgH97": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "description": "<h3>Rhododendron</h3><p>Mad honey is made by <a href=\"/pages/the-himalayan-giant-honey-bees\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"himalayan giant honey bees \">giant honeybees<strong>, </strong><em><strong>Apis Labroiosa</strong></em></a>, which gather nectar from rhododendron and various wildflowers.</p><h3>Psychoactive Benefits</h3><p>The grayanotoxin in mad honey leads to  potential <a href=\"/pages/mad-honey-effects\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mad honey effects\"><strong>psychoactive and hallucinatory effects</strong></a> when taken in high doses.</p><h3>Take Precautions</h3><p>Should be enjoyed in moderation due to its potency. It’s recommended to consult with a healthcare professional before use for a safe and positive experience.</p><h3>Bold and Smoky </h3><p>A smoky flavor with a distinct tingling sensation in the throat, surprising your tastebuds with unique experience.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_6HAnJU": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/madhoneybox.webp",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "",
            "image_width": "89.38%; grid-column:2/3;"
          }
        },
        "content_6jeMJd": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "description": "<h3>Honey Hunting</h3><p>Collected through traditional honey hunting process, where bees gather nectar from the rhododendron flowers, they transfer grayanotoxins into the mad honey honey.</p><h3>Low Glycemic Index</h3><p>Mad honey has a lower glycemic index, causing a gentler effect on blood sugar and being suitable for blood sugar management.</p><h3>Premium Packaging</h3><p><a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">Medicinal mad honey</a> comes in premium, eco-friendly packaging with elegant labels that highlight its origins, purity, and usage, revealing a luxurious, sustainable experience for wellness-focused consumers.</p><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "content_thgH97",
        "image_6HAnJU",
        "content_6jeMJd"
      ],
